Unless you have seen this book, chances are good you've never seen anything like it. John Holbo holds a Ph.D., is an Assistant Professor of Philosophy at the National University of Singapore, writes on, in or about philosophy of literature and literary theory, science fiction, fantasy, film, comics, books and blogs. 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

'Squid &amp; Owl'

Rhino bird, 2013, 106 pages

Written and Illustrated by John Holbo

